		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Three miniature heads of a chimera stare out from this headgear, granting you the multifaceted abilities of that beast.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Head Slot</b><b>:</b> Uncommon</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>You can use only one of the headdress's powers each day.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You score a critical hit against an enemy.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> That enemy takes ongoing 10 damage (save ends).</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You hit with a charge attack.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The charge attack deals 2d10 extra damage.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Minor Action)</b></p><p>You gain resist 15 acid, resist 15 cold, resist 15 lightning, or resist 15 poison (chosen when the item is created) until the end of the encounter.</p>",
